{"tid":709524,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"父親節上吊11歲男童　與死神搏鬥3日離世","createTime":"2018-06-20T05:25:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-20T11:26:19.000Z","uid":20933,"like":26,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"046559133a96074f454a48aadd91867c278b73ef","tid":709524,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T05:25:42.000Z","msg":"將軍澳一名11歲男生，在本周日（17日）父親節，於日出康城緻藍天晶巒寓所被尼龍繩纏頸狀似自縊，被姓潘(42歲)父親揭發報警。潘童被解下送院搶救，情況一直危殆，在與死神搏鬥3日，延至昨(19日)晚上7時22分離世，家人傷心欲絕。 <br />\n<br />\n消息指，潘就讀小學五年級，成績優秀和品行良好，家庭生活美滿，事前他毫無異樣，亦沒有遺書，最近他正學習童軍繩結法，故警方正循意外抑或自殺展開調查。"},{"pid":"9abddc0df347724fac56231131f3063ca7191615","tid":709524,"uid":63950,"like":5,"dislike":11,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T05:27:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"196a0f155867af9223995325bc6736238450fb72","tid":709524,"uid":22898,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T05:27:47.000Z","msg":"65%係屋企比壓力比得太勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e7aa760b904a0ae665588588c60fc00a94bc8a3","tid":709524,"uid":62646,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T05:30:44.000Z","msg":"成績優秀和品行良好，家庭生活美滿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 次次自殺都係咁寫"},{"pid":"bbfc0f5e3b00a2bc1a249426553d05735f220eb8","tid":709524,"uid":78384,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T05:36:49.000Z","msg":"與死神搏咩鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己自殺上吊"},{"pid":"4a4f83639eaa0fa972a5a4103028f81dec7b85fa","tid":709524,"uid":63414,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"quote":{"pid":"bbfc0f5e3b00a2bc1a249426553d05735f220eb8","tid":709524,"uid":78384,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T05:36:49.000Z","msg":"與死神搏咩鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己自殺上吊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T05:37:54.000Z","msg":"同醫生搏鬥"},{"pid":"99253a3727cdd9e341ee8acb6fb2c777ef1b37f2","tid":709524,"uid":14103,"